[Leptospirosis is a disease dogs should be vaccinated against. The article is reasonably comprehensive in its description. Whether you walk your dog in a dog park, visit friends with pets, or swim in the lake, your dog is at risk of this disease. Please contact your veterinarian about having your pet vaccinated.

The population is more mobile, and for many years vaccinations against lepto decreased, which left a na√Øve population all across the nation. A pet from one region can easily bring the disease to another region because of our highly mobile society. Please have your dog vaccinated against this disease. - Mod.TG

